</taxonomicName>
is a later taxonomic synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="L." box="[947,1071,1267,1294]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Rubus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="15" pageNumber="50" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="idaeus">
